**Rodrigues**: And! And then! Mr. Hopper and Ms. Lily go back to the pond. And-

**Dir. Silva**: And live happily ever after?

**Rodrigues**: Not really. Their life is boring. They're just frogs.

**Dir. Silva**: Huh.

**Rodrigues**: The story's more better if you don't expect it.

**Dir. Silva**: How about this story? It's called [[a href="https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/taboo"]][REDACTED][[/a]].

**Rodrigues**: [REDACTED]? That sounds boring.

//Fibrous protrusions emerge from Rodrigues and Silva's orifices.//

**Dir. Silva**: You need to be careful how you talk about [REDACTED] or you'll be punished.

**Rodrigues**: But you never told me what [REDACTED] is.

//The protrusions take root on the surfaces of the restroom. Extremities of the structure coalesce into tree branches.//

**Dir. Silva**: It's a magical forest where you have to stay on the dirt path.

**Rodrigues**: What? So I can't explore?

//The security system's conversation time threshold is exceeded, and Site-19 Command is notified. Tasers are fired, but they bounce off with a wooden thunk.//

**Dir. Silva**: You'll get lost if you do, and you never come ba- khk.

**Rodrigues**: And so- huh? Aunty? My eyes?! Eeeee! Mommeee-

//Roots consume the security camera and video feed is cut.//

